Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到时机成熟时才能出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀剑是不会选择对象的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用剑的人不够成熟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的刀锋也会跟着不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至会把不需要斩杀的人也给斩杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者你该保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你能够斩杀应该要斩杀的对象为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别解开它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月色真美丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿只会攻击鬼儿猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊先生  你的脚不痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是小樱  你拿的东西重不重？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我还拿得动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱  很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外！号外！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外！号外！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿袭击人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不会攻击一般市民的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市役所到底在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是要注意点为好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的鬼儿猎人狗狗搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做剑术的特训呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会饿着回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做好吃的东西等他们回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我给你的东西拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个蒙住眼睛然后回到店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼虽然能够在看见之前就作出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也只是偶然能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼则在看到之后才能作出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如让「两边都在看见之前作出反应」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途可以休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向路人问路也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在你能感觉到「气息」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把它解开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  带上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来你都是赤手空拳战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要先习惯拿剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黑钢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…「回去的时候帮买一些面粉回去～」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊先生拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙倒是挺会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得去买什么东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…花瓣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前与爸爸一起去过的国家中所看见的花很像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「樱」的花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小樱同名的花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  狗狗只回来了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  谢谢你帮忙买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请店里的人送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…小狼君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在训练中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离店还很远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我开始有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生命的物体和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是两种都有气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无生命的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是没有生命的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却追上来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才差点就被那家伙给干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴着它做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在练习剑术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  打搅到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果刚才那样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会被那个鬼儿杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  您好像也用剑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「您」  太见外了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我名字吧  我已经跟你报过名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…你不会是忘记了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙王也是用剑战斗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙可是最能产生「在战斗」的感觉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像护刃的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是像苏摩和草薙那样的特殊武器虽然也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还是想把要打倒的对手的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过剑用手去感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很期待能遇到我还不知道的劲敌哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了能和这样的对手战斗而变强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打倒了那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上还是会有更强的家伙出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要以此为目标走下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能变得越来越强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找到的是不可思议的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是未知的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算找到了以往不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也还会有更多我既没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没听过的不可思议之物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能一点一点地知道这些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有必须要取回的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下定决心一定要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想变强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越中意你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱  表情真好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君回来以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把好吃的给他拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人行道上好像都没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鬼儿现在开始袭击一般市民了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个东西想给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和我一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让那个公主一个人看店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好好特训过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经能独当一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:43.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時の向こう  風の町へ  ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:43.88,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}时间的对面是风吹拂过的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.66,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}連れて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.66,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}随之而去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:58.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}白い花の夢  かなえて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:58.89,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}满足那如同白色花朵般的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:10.16,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時の向こう  風の町へ  ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:10.16,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}时间的对面是风吹拂过的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:15.25,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}連れて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:15.25,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}随之而去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:24.54,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}白い花の夢  かなえて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:24.54,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}满足那如同白色花朵般的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美的歌声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要到什么地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用拜托什么人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:36.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い指で  この手をとり  ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:36.28,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}用宽大的手来指点询问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是黑碰的话就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我可是一直在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够被谁带走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.12,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠い道を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.12,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}指向遥远的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:51.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}導いて不思議の  あなたの  傍へ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:51.32,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}不可思议地陪伴在你的身边进行指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又会被你讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…黑狗狗  也抱抱摩可拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:14:00.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その歌声さえない  昼差があり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:14:00.72,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}那昼夜不绝的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:07.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目覚めて二人は一つになり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:07.15,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}使两人觉醒并合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:17.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せの意味を  始まってしるのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:17.35,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8\fs23}开始知晓那幸福的意味了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君他们回来之前要继续努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:24.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}連れて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:24.34,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an8\fs23}随之而去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想给我看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再不回去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿离店里很近  没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们新品种的鬼儿的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥  你还真是急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啊  织叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过新品种的鬼儿的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在这里唱歌的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为这里是我的店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意请客吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我就告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我见到的新品种的鬼儿的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱都国里的鬼儿为了让鬼儿猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不误伤到一般民众
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有都是异型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:16:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那只鬼儿有着人的形体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个漂亮的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新品种的鬼儿是人形的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你怎么知道他是鬼儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个国家里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了小争执和吵架之类的以外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在人类间的冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他却操纵着鬼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说鬼儿的同伴也是鬼儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新品种的鬼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知从哪里获得了很大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织叶小姐  那边的客人有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我知道的就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织叶小姐刚才说的话很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「樱都国里的鬼儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「为了让鬼儿猎人不误伤到一般民众」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「所有都是异型」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿是故意制造出来的东西  是这么一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这个国家的鬼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被管理着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为鬼儿猎人的靶子一样的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市役所能掌握鬼儿的动向的缘故就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鬼儿猎人不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近鬼儿的行动开始变的奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是被管理着的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变这个状况的人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是幻化成人形的新品种的鬼儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个鬼儿所持有的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不知从哪里获得了很大的力量」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是小樱的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的等级提升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就相当难以控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想控制就要有特别的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去吃巧克力蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别的什么蛋糕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你觉得哪种好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小小的猫咪」小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我看的就是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前的广场上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有樱都国最大的樱花树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  「小小的猫咪」小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小小的猫咪」小姐——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛就在这前面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给「小小的狗狗」看广场的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼儿出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种等级的鬼儿  为什么会这么强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么砍还是会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  有人抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个是稍有名气的鬼儿猎人耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:21:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是传言所说的新品种的鬼儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星史郎先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星史郎先生会在这个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到新品种鬼儿的小狼变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼好像和那个新品种的鬼儿好像有什么关联
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.65,0:24:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到新的情报的小狼和黑钢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.92,0:24:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又向新的地方进发了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请继续期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.08,0:24:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹不去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回登场的丝茉茉和琴子会让人期待不已！


